<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV36">
<l>āṭakatta pūṇmulaiya cōtaiyāycci piḷḷaiyāyc</l>
<l>cāṭutaittōr puḷḷatāvi kaḷḷatāya pēymakaḷ</l>
<l>vīṭavaitta veyyakoṅkai yaiyapāla mutucey</l>
<l>tāṭakakkai mātarvā yamutamuṇṭa teṉkolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Becoming the child of the cowherdess Yaśodā with breasts [adorned] with gold jewels,</l>
<l>[You] kicked the cart, drinking the doubtful milk from the cruel breasts</l>
<l rend="indent">placed [into Your mouth]</l>
<l>so that the sly demoness with a bird’s spirit perished.</l>
<l>How [then] did [You] enjoy the nectar from the mouths of women</l>
<l rend="indent">with gold[en bracelets] around [their] wrists?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
